Hello! I have two profiles. I would like to eliminate one but I do not know.
The original site of the Juhász Éva  (Táncoslábú Silver Schnauzer). I use it and keep it.

replies.message: Hi, JJuhász. It's against the Facebook Community Standards to maintain more than one personal account. You can learn how to delete your account here: http://bit.ly/2e9Kyh4. -Rhea
